{"tid":368154,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好似我咁 人生好似好空虛","createTime":"2017-08-21T10:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T12:03:43.000Z","uid":105727,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b662e9052b5ef42e2e07c56dcd361590df674b","tid":368154,"uid":105727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:36:14.000Z","msg":"已經單身左兩年<br />\n曾經會好想拍拖 快d出pool<br />\n不斷參加興趣班 玩交友app<br />\n希望可以識到適合自己嘅另一半<br />\n<br />\n同過幾個異性出街食下飯<br />\n但好多都唔夾<br />\n夾得黎我又鍾意嘅 但人地唔鍾意我<br />\n自自然然就冇再諗過要識人<br />\n拍拖、出pool嘅念頭亦無咗<br />\n<br />\n去到而家 反而一個人會好自在<br />\n朋友問仲想唔想識人、拍拖<br />\n其實都會 但唔會好渴望<br />\n因為真係好攰 唔想再尋尋覓覓<br />\n講得好聽d就係無欲無求<br />\n但其實個生活好空虛<br />\n究竟有冇人好似我咁?<br />\n定係得我一個咁唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59026d26c2d4319b4b4e4ece37c97ebc85e8c136","tid":368154,"uid":2615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"得閒揼下邪骨叫下雞算啦"},{"pid":"4d2eef446ea6cbba1fb99dc303b62b1c117909fb","tid":368154,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得閒揼下邪骨叫下雞算啦</blockquote><br />\n啱呀"},{"pid":"731d23bf0a36f31c2f278b16a55d3a5dc3cd5252","tid":368154,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"又係d搵唔到女就話空虛<br />\n有女你就會充實d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fdd0af94510ba934122274e48d0ed8245f2c6b6","tid":368154,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係d搵唔到女就話空虛<br />\n有女你就會充實d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有女就煩，又要時間，又要錢"},{"pid":"1e584691db9b99a1e5bb201ac0109ed79be347e8","tid":368154,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"標題就心生空虛<br />\n入到黎就講拍拖<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"af70ebb524fde8bf7a239f1487bdaf96e1e768ab","tid":368154,"uid":7